title: Week 6 Start or Sit! (10/17 Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Let's take one final look at the backup RBs - Chuba Hubbard, Darrel Williams, Devontae Booker, Khalil Herbert and Alex Collins - and where they stand this week. We'll also review the injured WRs who are likely to play and answer your questions. 
Follow our FFT team on Twitter: @FFToday, @AdamAizer, @JameyEisenberg, @daverichard, @heathcummingssr, @ctowerscbs, @BenSchragg
